      "content": "that's a good start for the tone. can u make it a bit more detailed though? like, instead of just saying they are \"prone to chaos,\" maybe have him describe a specific situation where he thinks local customs are actually hindering their progress compared to british law or science. it would help make the \"necessity\" of the empire feel more grounded in his logic.",
